# @VERSION spec:gdla v:0.1.0 generated:2026-04-15 source:api-agent
# Project Atlas — Atlas Finance API v2.2 (mid-build)

@D atlas-finance-api|Atlas finance API mid-build snapshot — adds reconciliation gate drill-down|2.2.0|https://api.acme.internal/finance/v2

@AUTH bearer|JWT bearer issued by Acme SSO|Authorization

@S ReconciliationGate|Per-period gate detail
 period|string|required||YYYY-MM
 threshold|number|required||Variance threshold
 currentVariance|number|required||Current variance value
 status|string|required||OPEN|CLOSED|GATED|WAIVED
 lastEvaluatedAt|string|required|date-time|Last evaluation timestamp

@S GateExplanation|Human-readable explanation for a gate decision
 period|string|required||YYYY-MM
 verdict|string|required||PASS|FAIL
 reasons|string|required||Pipe-delimited reason list
 nextActions|string|||Suggested next steps for finance ops

@EP GET /reconciliation/{period}/gate|Returns current gate state|getReconGate
@EP GET /reconciliation/{period}/gate/explain|Returns human-readable gate explanation|explainReconGate
@EP POST /reconciliation/{period}/gate/waive|Manually waives the gate (with audit)|waiveReconGate

@R GateExplanation -> ReconciliationGate|references|GateExplanation refers to a specific gate state
